9
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:34,320
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala.

10
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:40,240
[SPEAKER_00] Lana, inače možda ne znaju to svi, ali evo ga., ja sam tvoj kum.

11
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:46,079
