[SPEAKER_00] Koliko si ti tad imala?

35
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bila negdje 5-6-8.

36
00:03:21,599 --> 00:03:22,479
[SPEAKER_00] 5-6-8.

37
00:03:22,879 --> 00:03:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo može dragi.

38
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:26,800
